title: Listen to Flume’s New Skin Companion EP II
text:
Listen to Flume’s New Skin Companion EP II Featuring “Enough” with Pusha T Flume Photo by C Flanigan/Getty Images 
Flume has released a follow-up EP to his album Skin and EP Skin Companion , the aptly titled Skin Companion EP II . Listen to the new EP—including a collaboration with Pusha T called “Enough”—below. The Australian producer recently took home the Grammy award for Best Dance/Electronica Album for Skin . 
Revisit Flume’s video for “Some Minds” featuring Andrew Wyatt on Pitchfork.tv: Artists In This Story
